Package org.openstreetmap.josm.plugins.mapillary.actions

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MapillaryDownloadAction
    Action that triggers the plugin.
    MapillaryDownloadViewAction
    If in manual mode, downloads all the images in the current view.
    MapillaryExportAction
    Action that launches a MapillaryExportDialog and lets you export the images.
    MapillaryImportAction
    Imports a set of picture files into JOSM.
    MapillaryImportIntoSequenceAction
    Imports a set of images and puts them in a single MapillarySequence.
    MapillaryJoinAction
    Changes the mode of the Layer, from Select mode to Join mode and viceversa.
    MapillaryWalkAction
    Walks forward at a given interval.
    MapillaryZoomAction
    Zooms to the currently selected image.
